spanGrp.span: Me, I'm called Gemulsa of Baheeba
Me, I remember only a short story
qay asimjeeg gend someeg gwand somega
In the old days the Asimjeeg were in Someega, they were in Someega
Zamani waasimjeega tupo Somega, wapo Somega
Later they were eaten by a snake
araeijood ni qohiit buneed qok aa qwanung'wew ga ng'ay
This snake ate people until there were very few
Huyo nyoka alikula watu mpaka wakabaki wachache
They were helped by the medicine men
This snake who finished the Asimjeeg
iisin aa gaheed hanan qayiiny kumbkumbees ni gidap qay asimjeeg qowasch sang' diya
When I grew up I heard too "You Asimjeeg were very many"
Nilipokua pia nikasikia kuwa ninyi waasimjeega mlikuwa wengi sana
"But you were finished by a snake"
We were helped by the medicine men against this snake
Tukasaidiwa na Waganga kwa huyo nyoka
kwa hiyo anin gad damosh hanan qahoon ni qay ba murumbajeegan
So me I am still saying these prayers of the old days with the medicine men
Kwa hiyo mimi bado naomba hiyo dua ya zamani ya waganga
So that it helps us even now
qo kumbukumb eed ja erukwisiin ar deebugas gabung'nan hiiji
So that it is a memory that we tell even our children, I'll finish here
Iwe kumbukumbu ambao tutawahadithia hata watoto wetu naishia hapo
